lead_paragraph: Paul George scored 30 points, including Indiana's final 12 of the game to rally the Pacers to a 115-108 victory over the Los Angeles Lakers on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: George Scores 30, Including Pacers' Last 12 to Beat Lakers
